Enköping.title: Enköping
Enköping.byline: Enköping is a city in western Uppland in Sweden with about 20,000 inhabitants, branding itself "Sweden's nearest city".

Enkhuizen.title: Enkhuizen
Enkhuizen.byline: The small city of Enkhuizen is an old Dutch harbour town, and one of the most prominent ones of the Dutch Golden Age.
